      "code_id": "fc552f56-48cb-4e09-bc3b-f4ba5073555f",
      "code_content": "list_a = [('apple', 'banana', 'orange', 'grapes'), ('cricket', 'football', 'hockey'), ('car', 'bicycle', 'bus')]\n\nn = int(input())\nnew_list = []\n\nfor i in range(n):\n    index = input().split()\n    tuple_index = int(index[0])\n    value_index = int(index[1])\n    value = list_a[tuple_index][value_index]\n    new_list.append(value)\n\nprint(new_list)\n",
